{"parse":{"title":"Operation Thrividha Balaya","pageid":22763669,"revid":851148333,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p>\n<table class=\"infobox vevent\" style=\"width:25.5em;border-spacing:2px;\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"summary\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Operation Thrividha Balaya</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#DCDCDC;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;\">Part of <a href=\"/wiki/Sri_Lankan_Civil_War\" title=\"Sri Lankan Civil War\">Sri Lankan Civil War</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\"><table style=\"width:100%;margin:0;padding:0;border:0\"><tbody><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Date</th><td>13 September 1990</td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Location</th><td><span class=\"location\"><a href=\"/wiki/Jaffna\" title=\"Jaffna\">Jaffna</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Sri_Lanka\" title=\"Sri Lanka\">Sri Lanka</a></span></td></tr><tr><th style=\"padding-right:1em\">Result</th><td>\nSri Lankan Military succeeds in breaking the siege at Jaffna Fort</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Belligerents</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\n<span class=\"flagicon\"><a href=\"/wiki/Sri_Lanka\" title=\"Sri Lanka\"><img alt=\"Sri Lanka\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg/25px-Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg.png\" width=\"25\" height=\"13\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg/38px-Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/11/Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg/50px-Flag_of_Sri_Lanka.svg.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1200\" data-file-height=\"600\" /></a></span> <a href=\"/wiki/Sri_Lankan_Military\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sri Lankan Military\">Sri Lankan Military</a></td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/LTTE\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"LTTE\">LTTE</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;font-size:110%;\">Commanders and leaders</th></tr><tr><td style=\"width:50%;border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">\nMaj. Gen <a href=\"/wiki/Denzil_Kobbekaduwa\" title=\"Denzil Kobbekaduwa\">Denzil Kobbekaduwa</a></td><td style=\"width:50%;padding-left:0.25em\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/Vellupillai_Prabhakaran\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Vellupillai Prabhakaran\">Vellupillai Prabhakaran</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Eelam_War_II\" style=\"margin:0;float:right;clear:right;width:25.5em;margin-bottom:0.5em;margin-left:1em;;padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color:#C3D6EF;\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Campaignbox_Eelam_War_II\" title=\"Template:Campaignbox Eelam War II\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Campaignbox_Eelam_War_II\" title=\"Template talk:Campaignbox Eelam War II\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Campaignbox_Eelam_War_II&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\" style=\";background-color:#C3D6EF;;background:none transparent;bo